videos.description: Emmett Naar is 2-for-2 from the 3-point line in the first half.
videos.headline: Naar pulls up for the easy 3

videos.description: Jock Landale muscles through the paint for the hook shot and is fouled on the play by Juwan Gray.
videos.headline: Landale creates 3-point play

videos.description: Tyler Williams closes the gap on Saint Mary's with another 3-pointer for the Toreros.
videos.headline: San Diego inching closer by way of the 3 ball

videos.description: San Diego's Isaiah Wright makes it a 2-point game after sinking a 3-pointer from the corner.
videos.headline: Wright pulls up for the deep 3
